psalm.text:
[[Ps 147,12]]Glorify the LORD, O Jerusalem; 
praise your God, O Zion.
[[Ps 147,13]]For he has strengthened the bars of your gates; 
he has blessed your children within you.

[[Ps 147,15]]He sends forth his command to the earth; 
swiftly runs his word!
[[Ps 147,16]]He spreads snow like wool; 
frost he strews like ashes.

[[Ps 147,19]]He has proclaimed his word to Jacob, 
his statutes and his ordinances to Israel.
[[Ps 147,20]]He has not done thus for any other nation; 
his ordinances he has not made known to them. Alleluia
